Patch Set 4: Code-Review-1

Having 127.0.0.1 here suggests that it is the default value.

Looking at the glance_store code (remember, glance_store is now a separate git repository):

 $ grep -r DEFAULT_ADDR glance_store/
 glance_store/_drivers/sheepdog.py:DEFAULT_ADDR = 'localhost'

It seems that the default value is 'localhost'.

It's a bit painful, but what we may need to do is:

1) submit a patch to glance_store to change the default value to 127.0.0.1
2) wait for a new release of glance_store
3) update this patch with an additional change to "requirements.txt" to depend on the new version of glance_store
